<li>Higginbotham, A. Leon, Jr. <i>In the Matter of Color: Race and the American Legal Process: The Colonial Period.</i> Oxford University Press, 1978. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0195027450" class="internal">ISBN 0-19-502745-0</a></li>
<li>Horton, James Oliver and Horton, Lois E. <i>Slavery and the Making of America.</i> (2005) <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/019517903X" class="internal">ISBN 0-19-517903-X</a></li>
<li>Kolchin, Peter. <i>American Slavery, 1619-1877</i> Hill and Wang, 1993. Survey</li>
