nic Council">National Pan-Hellenic Council (NPHC)</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/The_Links,_Incorporated" title="The Links, Incorporated">The&#160;Links</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/National_Council_of_Negro_Women" title="National Council of Negro Women">National Council of Negro Women (NCNW)</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Ebony_Experiment" title="Ebony Experiment">Ebony Experiment</a></span></div>
